lead_paragraph: Deonte Burton launched soft, feathery jumpers from the perimeter and was just as effective muscling his way to the basket when he found that more to his and No. 21 Iowa State's advantage.

headline.print_headline: Burton Scores 21, No. 21 Iowa State Beats Miami 73-56
